15.40	Battle_of_Lundy's_Lane	Battle of Lundy's Lane	The Battle of Lundy's Lane (also known as the Battle of Niagara Falls) was a battle of the Anglo-American War of 1812, which took place on 25 July 1814, in present-day Niagara Falls, Ontario. It was one of the bloodiest battles of the war, and one of the deadliest battles ever fought on Canadian soil.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/6c/Battle_of_Lundys_Lane.jpg/300px-Battle_of_Lundys_Lane.jpg
